Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 127th Weekly Dose of Optimism. We have=
 an out-of-this-world edition for you this week =E2=80=94 tons of space new=
s, Wooly Mammoths, AI tutors, AI material models, massive Anudril factories=
