-size: 16px;margin: 0;">Licensing its genetic engineering technologies and =
tools developed during de-extinction efforts to other companies and researc=
hers for endangered species conservation, gene editing applications in agri=
culture and livestock, and medical and pharmaceutical applications. </p></l=
i><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55);li=
